943	0001001900040003	4	0	Status	<p><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Your status on ou reflects your level of engagement and the trust you have earned using the platform. Your status is measured in points, and you earn and lose points by performing actions on ou.</span><br></p>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Your status increases when:</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">You successfully complete Tasks (points depend on the task)</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">High priority tasks are 10 points</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Medium priority are 5 points</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Low priority are 2 points</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Ideas &amp; Bugs you create are accepted by the related product team</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Your accepted Ideas &amp; Bugs are upvoted</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">As a Manager or Admin of a product (requires at least “Product Bee” status), Tasks that you create are claimed and completed</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">You invite a user and they successfully register on ou</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">The user you invited complete their first task</span><br></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Your status decreases when:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">You claim Tasks and do not complete them successfully</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">You receive a warning for violating terms of use</span><br></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">Some ou functionality, such as the ability to claim paid Tasks or having a Public Portfolio of your work, requires a particular status. Ultimately, the more you use ou.com in a constructive way, the more points you earn, the higher your status and the more privileges you unlock.</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Arial;">How do points, status and privileges relate?</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<img src="/images/attachments/2021-04-17 23:51:04 131307a6.png" alt="undefined" style="height: auto;width: 100%"/>\n<p><br></p>\n		\N
