8	2021-05-25 06:49:26.506468+00	2021-05-25 06:49:26.506503+00	d6c51ad9-2ef1-489a-868e-12115977ca3c	Ability to download Product Data Sheet (PDF)	\N	<p>The ability to enable a link "download Data Sheet (PDF)" on the product page that creates an attractive PDF summary of the products and its capabilities at that point in time. This will help to ensure the information on products / capabilities is complete and enable people, including less technical users of ou, to get an overview of a product that they can read in a familiar format.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Some examples to illustrate what can be produced:</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.slideshare.net/TDSmaker/software-datasheet-template" target="_blank">https://www.slideshare.net/TDSmaker/software-datasheet-template</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.prosoft-technology.com/content/download/4307/30796/version/1/file/EZ_ASCE_Datasheet.pdf" target="_blank">https://www.prosoft-technology.com/content/download/4307/30796/version/1/file/EZ_ASCE_Datasheet.pdf</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n	8d5c116e-fbdd-4065-af07-e08abca21563	3	102	\N	0
