21	2021-02-15 17:16:50.93+00	2021-04-14 13:43:21.046065+00	Implement Active users list UI in the Admin section	<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Task description</span></h2>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Implement updated Active Users List UI. This section allows admin to view the Active users list and filter them based on the parameters selected</span></p>\n<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Interactive prototype</span></h2>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/VSTQ2MSMHTE#/screens/382949532</span></p>\n<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Definition of done</span></h2>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User is able to view the Active Users list, including (Design -</span><a href="https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/VSTQ2MSMHTE#/screens/382949532"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/VSTQ2MSMHTE#/screens/382949532</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">)</span></li>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Username</span></li>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User can go to a user details screen by clicking on the username in the list</span></li>\n</ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Display Name</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Last Login date and time</span></li>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">if last login time is less than 1 hour the time should be displayed time in minutes (rounded)</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">if last login time is between 1 hour and 1 day time should be displayed in hours (rounded)</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">if last login time is between 1 day and 7 days, time should be displayed in days (rounded)</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">if time is more than 7 days, time should be displayed in weeks (rounded)</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">if user did not log in yet, Last Login value should be set to "Didn't login yet"</span></li>\n</ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Auth method can be</span></li>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">"2FA" if 2-factor authentication is enabled</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">SFA if 2-factor authentication is disabled</span></li>\n</ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Groups</span></li>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Groups tab should be displaying all the groups this member is a part of</span></li>\n</ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User has the following quick actions which can be applied to each of the user records in the list:</span></li>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Edit</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Takes to the user profile page which can be edited&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Change password</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Leads to Change Password screen for a selected user</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Consents and Data trasnfer</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Takes to the Consents and Data Transfer screen for a selected user</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lock</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TBD</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Deactivate users</span>