/ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User is able to filter Active users by Group (Design:</span><a href="https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/VSTQ2MSMHTE#/screens/382949533"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/VSTQ2MSMHTE#/screens/382949533</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">)</span></li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User has "Only Admins" and "Only Locked" filters always visible</span></li>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User can select one or more groups to filter active users by</span></li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once a filter is enabled, user can clear the selection or remove each individual filter</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mass selection and actions</span></li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Designs:</span></li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/TVU4L22NQR5#/screens"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/VSTQ2MSMHTE#/screens/382949533</span></a></li>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/UAU4L2BVYT6#/screens"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/UAU4L2BVYT6#/screens</span></a></li>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/GUU4L2X6ENK#/screens</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User can select single or multiple entry via a checkbox</span></li>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User has then mass deactivate and mass delete entries from the list</span></li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">If &ldquo