5	Implement "Contribution Guide" capability	<p>Contributors need to receive the right guidance on how to contribute. Core teams are responsible for crafting these guidelines and adding them to the relevant tasks. For every product, there can multiple guidelines crafted e.g. for UI/UX design, frontend development, backend development, QA, etc..</p>\n<p>Contribution Guide is a long text or simply a document which can be set by core teams in the "Product Setting" tab &gt; "Contribution" tab &gt; "Contribution Guides".</p>\n<p><img src="https://trello-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/60061159f2061b6a1fa64094/604df5ba7da2c77092089fe9/2130340f4d05fa0b670c2281a6ad8ee1/image.png" alt="undefined" style="height: undefined;width: undefined"/></p>\n<p>When they tab on creating a guide, they see a Contribution Guide creation modal which includes these fields: "Guide Title*" (max 60 chars and required) ,"Guide Description*" (Long text format and we should use the same WYSISYG editor as task description), and a "Skills" (it's optional and multiple skills can be selected, we need to implement it similar to the Skills Required field in the task creation modal where you can search for all the available skills on OU)</p>\n<p><img src="https://trello-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/60061159f2061b6a1fa64094/604df5ba7da2c77092089fe9/32cf0cc832545aabca93819fbe00f7fe/image.png" alt="undefined" style="height: undefined;width: undefined"/></p>\n<p>Once the guides will be added, they will be shown in the table format in the setting</p>\n<p><img src="https://trello-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/60061159f2061b6a1fa64094/604df5ba7da2c77092089fe9/a1ae9a51cad435f9896631d2df6ff0bc/image.png" alt="undefined" style="height: undefined;width: undefined"/></p>\n<p>In the task creation modal, there needs to be a dropdown field added which is called "Contribution Guide" and it should be optional. Product admin or manager can pick a guide from the drop down values which are titles of the existing guides.</p>\n<p>Once the task is created, the Contributing Guide is added to the task detail page, above the Blocked By section in a similar design.</p>\n<p><img src="https://trello-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/604df5ba7da2c77092089fe9/976x1086/f6907bdbdb24ec2e7d0e8583db8d2d2c/image.png" alt="undefined" style="height: undefined;width: undefined"/></p>\n	Contribution Guide is a document which outlines guiding information on how to set up the system for the contributions, what are the guidelines for the delivered works to be approved, where the work needs to be delivered, etc.	4	{}	f	f	0	8	t	{"username": "john-smith", "full_name": "Farbod (Admin of OU & Contributor of AM)"}	{"username": "farbod", "full_name": "Farbod Saraf"}	{"username": "john-smith", "full_name": "Farbod (Admin of OU & Contributor of AM)"}	3	{"id": 58, "kind": 0, "task": 90, "person": 8}	{"username": "nazar", "full_name": "Nazar Revutsky"}	f	4	156	90	1133c1d1-b5bf-47d4-8a50-3da227168474	{"name": "ou Product Factory", "slug": "ou-product-factory", "owner": "meta", "website": "https://ou.com", "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OWXVryhdoVA", "detail_url": null}	d3d50522-9132-4c5a-b72e-9a36314cc823	{"id": 4, "name": "Prepare OU for Stackoverflow launch", "status": 1, "product": 3, "video_url": null, "description": "<p>A soft launch of ou by listing ads Stackoverflow to seek contributors for the Product Factory Platform.</p>\\n"}	{"id": 156, "name": "Contributing guidelines", "path": "0001001A000D0001", "depth": 4, "numchild": 0, "video_link": "", "description": ""}	t	\N
